ex.parser
Class BestParser

java.lang.Object
  ex.parser.Parser
      ex.parser.BestParser

public class BestParser
extends Parser

Implements a parser that takes the best AC first, and successively adds neighboring ACs, creating still larger ICs. This is repeated for all ACs.
